data.description: Buyer could not sell her home so we are back on the market. All inspection items addressed! This home is located in the very desirable Yellow Bluff Landing neighborhood featuring the Amelia floor plan.  SOLAR being fully paid off is a huge feature especially with the rising cost of energy bills! This home is on a cul-de-sac with a beautifully shaded, fenced back yard.   Upgrades:  architectural shingles, stucco and natural ledgestone features, custom natural entry shower w/ tub in master bedroom, finished 2 car garage, 42'' upper cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances.  Fabulous amenities with fun for the entire family!!!
